<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>성격 테스트 결과 - 앙상블 스타즈</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        :root {
            --main-color: #3b82f6;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
            --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .result-box {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: popIn 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.36, 0, 0.66, 1);
        }
        
        .result-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--main-color), #ff3399);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .chemistry-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
        
        .result-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        
        .result-body {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .partner-name {
            font-size: 2.2em;
            color: var(--main-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .partner-unit {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--main-color), #ff3399);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .personality-section {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--main-color);
        }
        
        .personality-section h3 {
            color: var(--main-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .personality-section p {
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }
        
        .description-section {
            background: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4da6ff;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .description-section strong {
            color: #0055aa;
        }
        
        .compatibility-scores {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .score-item {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .score-label {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .score-bar {
            background: #e0e0e0;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .score-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--main-color), #ff3399);
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: width 0.6s ease;
        }
        
        .score-value {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: var(--main-color);
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 150px;
            padding: 14px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--main-color), #ff3399);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.3);
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background: white;
            color: var(--main-color);
            border: 2px solid var(--main-color);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--main-color);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        
        @keyframes popIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.9) translateY(20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* 태블릿 및 모바일 최적화 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                max-width: 100%;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .result-box {
                border-radius: 20px;
            }

            .result-header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .result-body {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .chemistry-badge {
                font-size: 1em;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .result-header h2 {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
            
            .partner-name {
                font-size: 1.8em;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            .partner-unit {
                font-size: 0.9em;
                padding: 6px 16px;
            }

            .personality-section,
            .description-section {
                padding: 15px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .personality-section h3 {
                font-size: 1em;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }

            .personality-section p {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }

            .description-section {
                font-size: 0.9em;
            }
            
            .compatibility-scores {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 12px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .score-item {
                padding: 12px;
            }

            .score-label {
                font-size: 0.85em;
                margin-bottom: 6px;
            }

            .score-value {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }
            
            .buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
                margin-top: 25px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                min-width: auto;
                padding: 12px 16px;
                font-size: 0.95em;
            }

            img[alt] {
                max-width: 200px !important;
                height: 250px !important;
                margin-bottom: 25px !important;
            }

            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }
        }

        /* 작은 모바일 (480px 이하) */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .result-box {
                border-radius: 15px;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.1);
            }

            .result-header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .result-body {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }

            .chemistry-badge {
                font-size: 0.9em;
                padding: 8px 16px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .result-header h2 {
                font-size: 1em;
                margin-bottom: 8px;
            }
            
            .partner-name {
                font-size: 1.5em;
                margin-bottom: 6px;
            }

            .partner-unit {
                font-size: 0.85em;
                padding: 5px 14px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .personality-section,
            .description-section {
                padding: 12px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .personality-section h3 {
                font-size: 0.95em;
                margin-bottom: 6px;
            }

            .personality-section p {
                font-size: 0.85em;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }

            .description-section {
                font-size: 0.85em;
                line-height: 1.6;
                padding: 12px;
            }
            
            .compatibility-scores {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 18px;
            }

            .score-item {
                padding: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }

            .score-label {
                font-size: 0.8em;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }

            .score-bar {
                height: 6px;
                margin-bottom: 6px;
            }

            .score-value {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            
            .buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 8px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }
            
            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 11px 14px;
                font-size: 0.9em;
                border-radius: 20px;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 11px 14px;
                font-size: 0.9em;
                border-radius: 20px;
            }

            img[alt] {
                max-width: 160px !important;
                height: 200px !important;
                margin-bottom: 20px !important;
                border-radius: 12px !important;
            }

            body {
                padding: 8px;
            }
        }

        /* 강아지 데코레이션 */
        .dog-decoration {
            position: fixed;
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .dog-top-right {
            top: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
        }

        .dog-bottom-left {
            bottom: 40px;
            left: 30px;
            width: 75px;
            height: 75px;
            opacity: 0.6;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(-2deg);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        (function(){
            const Audioctx = window.AudioContext || window.webkitAudioContext;
            let ctx;
            function getCtx(){ if(!ctx) ctx = new Audioctx(); return ctx; }

            function playChime(){
                const c = getCtx(); const now = c.currentTime;
                const master = c.createGain(); master.connect(c.destination);
                master.gain.setValueAtTime(0, now);
                master.gain.linearRampToValueAtTime(0.07, now + 0.02);
                master.gain.linearRampToValueAtTime(0, now + 0.9);

                const freqs = [440, 660, 880];
                freqs.forEach((f,i)=>{
                    const o = c.createOscillator(); o.type='triangle'; o.frequency.setValueAtTime(f, now + i*0.09);
                    o.connect(master); o.start(now + i*0.09); o.stop(now + i*0.09 + 0.5);
                });
            }

            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', ()=>{
                try{ playChime(); }catch(e){}
            });
        })();
    </script>
    <!-- 강아지 데코레이션 -->
    <svg class="dog-decoration dog-top-right" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <ellipse cx="100" cy="110" rx="55" ry="58" fill="#fdd835" stroke="#f9a825" stroke-width="2"/>
        <ellipse cx="60" cy="55" rx="18" ry="35" fill="#f9a825" stroke="#f57c00" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(-20 60 55)"/>
        <ellipse cx="62" cy="58" rx="10" ry="20" fill="#ffb74d" transform="rotate(-20 62 58)"/>
        <ellipse cx="140" cy="55" rx="18" ry="35" fill="#f9a825" stroke="#f57c00" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(20 140 55)"/>
        <ellipse cx="138" cy="58" rx="10" ry="20" fill="#ffb74d" transform="rotate(20 138 58)"/>
        <ellipse cx="100" cy="110" rx="8" ry="10" fill="#2c2c2c"/>
        <path d="M 100 110 Q 95 125 85 120" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M 100 110 Q 105 125 115 120" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="80" cy="95" r="8" fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <circle cx="80" cy="96" r="5" fill="#2c2c2c"/>
        <circle cx="81" cy="94" r="2" fill="white"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="95" r="8" fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="96" r="5" fill="#2c2c2c"/>
        <circle cx="121" cy="94" r="2" fill="white"/>
        <circle cx="55" cy="110" r="12" fill="#ffb74d" opacity="0.5"/>
        <circle cx="145" cy="110" r="12" fill="#ffb74d" opacity="0.5"/>
        <ellipse cx="100" cy="128" rx="6" ry="8" fill="#ff6b9d"/>
        <path d="M 145 125 Q 165 100 160 70" stroke="#f9a825" stroke-width="12" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M 145 125 Q 165 100 160 70" stroke="#fdd835" stroke-width="8" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.8"/>
    </svg>

    <svg class="dog-decoration dog-bottom-left" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <ellipse cx="100" cy="110" rx="55" ry="58" fill="#fdd835" stroke="#f9a825" stroke-width="2"/>
        <ellipse cx="60" cy="55" rx="18" ry="35" fill="#f9a825" stroke="#f57c00" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(-20 60 55)"/>
        <ellipse cx="62" cy="58" rx="10" ry="20" fill="#ffb74d" transform="rotate(-20 62 58)"/>
        <ellipse cx="140" cy="55" rx="18" ry="35" fill="#f9a825" stroke="#f57c00" stroke-width="2" transform="rotate(20 140 55)"/>
        <ellipse cx="138" cy="58" rx="10" ry="20" fill="#ffb74d" transform="rotate(20 138 58)"/>
        <ellipse cx="100" cy="110" rx="8" ry="10" fill="#2c2c2c"/>
        <path d="M 100 110 Q 95 125 85 120" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M 100 110 Q 105 125 115 120" stroke="#2c2c2c" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="80" cy="95" r="8" fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <circle cx="80" cy="96" r="5" fill="#2c2c2c"/>
        <circle cx="81" cy="94" r="2" fill="white"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="95" r="8" fill="white" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="96" r="5" fill="#2c2c2c"/>
        <circle cx="121" cy="94" r="2" fill="white"/>
        <circle cx="55" cy="110" r="12" fill="#ffb74d" opacity="0.5"/>
        <circle cx="145" cy="110" r="12" fill="#ffb74d" opacity="0.5"/>
        <ellipse cx="100" cy="128" rx="6" ry="8" fill="#ff6b9d"/>
    </svg>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="result-box">
            <div class="result-header">
                <div class="chemistry-badge">💕 Compatibility <%= chemistry %>%</div>
                <h2>당신의 운명의 파트너는?</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="result-body">
                <% if (partner.image) { %>
                    <img src="/images/<%= partner.image %>.png" alt="<%= partner.name %>" style="width: 100%; max-width: 250px; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 15px; margin: 0 auto 30px; display: block; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 0, 85, 0.15);">
                <% } %>
                <div class="partner-name"><%= partner.name %></div>
                <div class="partner-unit">[<%= partner.unit %>]</div>
                
                <div class="personality-section">
                    <h3>📖 캐릭터 성격</h3>
                    <p><%= partner.personality %></p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="description-section">
                    <strong>✨ 왜 당신과 맞을까요?</strong><br>
                    <%= partner.description %>
                </div>
                
                <div class="compatibility-scores">
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">당신의 열정</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (user.passion / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= user.passion.toFixed(1) %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">파트너의 열정</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (partner.scores.passion / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= partner.scores.passion %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">당신의 우아함</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (user.elegance / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= user.elegance.toFixed(1) %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">파트너의 우아함</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (partner.scores.elegance / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= partner.scores.elegance %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">당신의 지성</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (user.intelligence / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= user.intelligence.toFixed(1) %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">파트너의 지성</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (partner.scores.intelligence / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= partner.scores.intelligence %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">당신의 충성</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (user.loyalty / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= user.loyalty.toFixed(1) %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">파트너의 충성</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (partner.scores.loyalty / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= partner.scores.loyalty %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">당신의 자유</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (user.freedom / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= user.freedom.toFixed(1) %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="score-item">
                        <div class="score-label">파트너의 자유</div>
                        <div class="score-bar">
                            <div class="score-fill" style="width: <%= (partner.scores.freedom / 10) * 100 %>%"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="score-value"><%= partner.scores.freedom %>/10</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="buttons">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">다시 테스트하기</a>
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">처음으로</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
